        <p>Heroku is a cloud platform as a service or PaaS,
        supporting several programming languages. It is known for
        being one of the first cloud platforms, and has been in
        development since June 2007 when it supported the Ruby
        programming language, but since has added support for Java,
        Node.js, Scala, Clojure and Python and PHP. Heroku claims
        to offer the most NoSQL add-on solutions in the market
        today and that it introduced the 'polyglot platform', also
        it is recognized by many as one of the best cloud computer
        services available. It can be easily used through console
        and provide a very robust Web API.</p>

        <h2>Heroku Links</h2>

        <p>More information can be found at:</p>

        <ul>
            <li><a href="http://www.heroku.com/">Heroku Main
            Page</a></li>

