            <h3>Add-Ons Management</h3>

            <p>This procedure allows the user to manage the add-ons
            for a particular application, there are several actions
            to perform with add-ons, the options are: List all
            available add-ons for an app, list installed add-ons on
            an app, and there ir the possibility to install,
            upgrade and uninstall a specific add-on on an
            application.</p>

            <p>Some of the parameters are not required for all
            cases, however, the "required" specified fields cannot
            be omited.</p>
